flowchart LR
    START([Trigger]) --> VALIDATE[[Validate input]]

    subgraph PIPELINE[Processing pipeline]
        direction LR
        VALIDATE --> APPROVED{Approved?}
        APPROVED -->|Yes| EXECUTE[Execute workflow]
        EXECUTE --> STORE[(Write result)]
    end

    APPROVED -->|No| REJECT([Rejected])
    STORE --> COMPLETE([Complete])
